title: I'm Remarkable Workshop
description: A Google initiative empowering women and underrepresented groups to celebrate their achievements in the workplace and beyond. The 90 minute workshop will highlight to participants the importance of self promotion in their careers and provide them with the tools to start developing this skill.

title: I’m a BRAND - Personal Branding Workshop
description: The quintessential skill in the rapidly expanding  world of today - how you package yourself, communicate your unique skills and the value you bring to an organisation. Your personal brand is what people say about you when you are not in the room. The 45 minute session will teach you exactly that! How to build a reputation for yourself!

title: Flutter on Fire! - Flutter Codelab
description: Flutter, our savior to build mobile apps in record time allows you to create beautiful native apps on iOS and Android from a single codebase. Flutter facilitates Fast Development, Expressive and Flexible UI and Native Performance. What better than a hands-on on this! Ready. Code. Hot Reload!
